Learn the basics
Templates

Find a template that meets your needs. Reopen the panel from the More actions () menu when it's closed.

Slash commands

Type / to open a menu and insert content like tables, macros, and dates to your page as you go.

Table manipulation

Edit or format tables from the table borders, dropdown, and floating menu.

Image display

Select an image, then drag the handles to resize it, or use the floating menu to change its alignment.

Columns

Add a column to your page, then use the floating menu to switch between 2 or 3 column configurations.
